      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-gxn-flg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se codice a spazi                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-gxn-cod    =    spaces
                     go to let-arc-gxn-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
